ticle/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-138/0000018d-cc74-deb3-afdd-fff45f360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列机场管理局表示，美联航和达美航空将恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</link><description>虽然航空公司尚未正式宣布恢复飞往以色列的航班，但美联航网站已从 3 月起提供飞往以色列的机票 ■ 美国航空公司将于 10 月初停止飞往以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</guid></item><item><title>最新民意调查显示，大多数以色列人表示加沙不太可能取得“绝对胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</link><description>“绝对胜利”这个词是故意选择的，因为它已成为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理在新闻发布会和外语采访中喜欢用的词，尽管他不愿定义其实际含义</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛亲巴勒斯坦教职人员团体为分享带有反犹太主义图像的帖子而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</link><description>哈佛大学谴责了这张照片，并表示其管理委员会将从现在开始审查这些帖子。该大学写道：“我们以最强烈的措辞谴责这些帖子”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称联合国最高法院不应敦促以色列立即从巴勒斯坦声称拥有主权的土地上撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</link><description>在国际法院就以色列占领领土举行听证会的第三天，美国代表告诉专家组不要试图“通过针对仅关注某一方行为的问题的咨询意见”来解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军高级律师：一些士兵在加沙的行为已经“跨越了犯罪门槛”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</link><description>在给以色列国防军指挥官的一封信中，军法署署长指出，必须对那些“跨越犯罪门槛”的士兵采取行动，例如“在行动上不合理地使用武力、抢劫、掠夺私人财产和破坏平民财产”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</guid></item><item><title>撰写太空道德准则的以色列豪猪专家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</link><description>兹维·塞维尔教授曾踏遍非洲森林，为内塔尼亚胡封锁的天才和才华撰写了法案，与比尔·盖茨和安吉拉·默克尔交换了想法，并研究了伊朗人。因此，难怪他将自己的道德准则带到了联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</guid></item><item><title>承认巴勒斯坦国是对恐怖活动的奖励吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对人类的复杂性和历史的进程一无所知，希望让世界相信巴勒斯坦国只不过是“恐怖的奖励”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</link><description>21 岁的亚伯拉罕·沃瓦根上士在纳哈尔旅服役。沃加文 (Wogaven) 是内坦亚居民，身后留下父母和 11 个兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新报告称，哈马斯 10 月 7 日期间及之后的性暴力是“系统性和蓄意的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</link><description>以色列强奸危机中心协会发布了一份基于证词、采访和其他来源的报告，表明哈马斯的性暴力是“涉及系统性、有针对性的性虐待的明确行动策略”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</guid></item><item><title>无人机的黄金：大规模泄漏揭示了俄罗斯的伊朗沙赫德项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</link><description>文件揭示了售价 20 万美元的 Shahed 136 如何成为俄罗斯在乌克兰武库中的致命武器，以及先进型号的外观</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦真的“代表巴勒斯坦”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</link><description>从文学节到政治神职人员，加沙战争加剧了巴基斯坦对以色列本已过度的敌意。虽然崇尚美德的进步人士和反犹太主义伊斯兰主义者在庆祝哈马斯方面找到了共同点，但他们真正在做什么来拯救巴勒斯坦人的生命呢？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统用几句话抹去了他与以色列和犹太复国主义的所有热情联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</link><description>作为以色列的长期朋友和支持者，卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与纳粹针对犹太人的行动进行了比较，这让总统与以色列之间数十年的善意化为泡影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列空袭大马士革居民区，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</link><description>以色列尚未证实袭击事件，但叙利亚人权组织负责人表示，袭击事件与上个月在贝鲁特发生的哈马斯高级官员被暗杀事件类似</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷第二圣殿的奇怪石盒被发现。这是犹太洁食吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</link><description>这个盒子由石灰石制成，就像古代犹太家庭典型的石质厨具一样，盒子上有炭化痕迹——这是 2000 年前耶路撒冷被罗马人摧毁的痕迹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡来说，停滞是完美的环境。对于以色列来说，这意味着灾难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</link><description>尽管上周反对党因政府试图将卡西夫逐出议会而陷入内讧，但联盟成员的信心却在不断增强。尽管艾森科特比甘茨更激进，但他们都陷入了同一个陷阱</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-stagnation-is-the-perfect-environment-for-israel-it-spells-disaster/0000018d-c88b-ddae-a18f-ffbf6c030000</guid></item><item><title>在美国加大努力斡旋人质释放协议后，以色列持谨慎乐观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</link><description>几周以来，耶路撒冷首次出现了一些乐观情绪，认为美国谈判另一项协议的努力将取得成果。会谈目前集中在几个关键问题上，主要是以色列将释放的人质与巴勒斯坦囚犯的比例以及停火将持续多久</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 04:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-cautiously-optimistic-after-u-s-ramps-up-efforts-to-broker-a-hostage-release-deal/0000018d-c82a-ddae-a18f-ffbea2f30000</guid></item><item><title>法国：加沙的45名人质从卡塔尔斡旋的交易中获得药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</link><description>叙利亚报道以色列袭击大马士革住宅区 ■ 伊朗指责以色列破坏天然气管道 ■ 据报道以色列袭击加沙车辆造成人员伤亡 ■ 以色列国防军高级律师表示，有士兵参与战争犯罪行为 ■ 以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 03:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-live/qatar-says-medicine-delivered-to-hostages-u-s-vetoes-un-resolution-demanding-cease-fire/0000018d-c9ac-d09f-a3df-e9bcee6d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>